            <li><a class="external" href="https://kids.britannica.com/students/article/Steve-Jobs/311881" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steve Jobs - Student Encyclopedia (Ages 11 and up)</a></li>
            </ul>

    </div>
				</div>
			</div>

    	







































